", "dates": ["1957-04-04"], "description": ["Spring means many things Robins flowers budding r trees Forsythia but above all it usually makes us feel young at heart Believe me thats the way I felt the day I visited the 34 stores at Central Point The weather was ideal and the center electrified a hub of activity with everyone in the center busy as bees in a molasses barrel unpacking Spring Surprises If youre ready to take a tour lets go Fashions are my weakness too There are so many breath taking fashions tor women and children in a complete range of sizes and colors such as the high fashion shades Wisteria pink cloud heavenly blues yellow fluff surf green muted gray and those in ever popular blacks and navys Matching accessories and shoes were also spotlighted Youll find many of these fashions which are advertised in national magazines for the career girl or home maker at Central Point If your talent is designing or dressmaking youll find all the items you need to complete an ensemble plus sewing equipment Fashion is a mans world too Thats what I observed behind the scenes Everything the wellgroomed man or boy wears can be found at Central Point Now"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2025-04-13T07:01:25.282Z", "group": ["ndnp/ohi", "ohio-historical-society-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn88077733/1957-04-04/ed-1/?sp=8", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:ohi:batch_ohi_draco_ver02:data:sn88077733:00516993431:1957040401:0959/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=302&w=219", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:ohi:batch_ohi_draco_ver02:data:sn88077733:00516993431:1957040401:0959/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=605&w=438", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/ohi/batch_ohi_draco_ver02/data/sn88077733/00516993431/1957040401/0959.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 3, "language": ["english"], "location": ["franklin county", "united states", "